<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-PT">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Details | Creative Technologist</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/estilo.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <main>
        <section class="project-detail-hero">

            <a href="projects.html" class="back-link">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Projects
            </a>

            <div class="project-meta-top">
                <span class="badge-outline">UX/UI</span>
                <span class="dot-separator">•</span>
                <span class="year">2024</span>
            </div>

            <h1>Adidas Website</h1>

            <p class="project-description">Designed a concept website for Adidas, focused on creating a dynamic and
                engaging digital
                experience that reflects the brand’s energy, innovation, and sporty identity.</p>

            <div class="project-meta-bottom">
                <span><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> 4 months</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> 3 designers</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i> UX/UI Design</span>
            </div>

            <div class="project-actions">
                <a href="https://vodafone-ds.netlify.app/" class="btn-branco">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> View Live
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="project-hero-image">
                <img src="https://www.vodafone.com.au/images/oneapp/clm-and-support/phase-2/1414-my-vodafone-app-optin-hero-mobile.webp"
                    alt="AI Content Generator Dashboard" class="capa-detalhe">
            </div>

        </section>

        <section class="project-results-section">
            <div class="project-stats-grid">

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">30+</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">FRAMES</span>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">90%</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">REWORK</span>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">400+</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">COMPONENTS</span>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-challenge-solution">
            <div class="challenge-solution-grid">

                <div class="text-block">
                    <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i> The Challenge</h3>
                    <p>Vodafone needed a more consistent and scalable design approach across multiple digital products
                        and platforms. The main challenge was to unify different interfaces, reduce design
                        inconsistencies, and improve collaboration between design and development teams.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-block">
                    <h3><i class="fa-regular fa-lightbulb"></i> The Solution</h3>
                    <p>We developed a design system concept for Vodafone focused on scalability, consistency, and
                        efficiency. The system defines a structured library of reusable components, design patterns, and
                        UX guidelines that ensure a cohesive experience across all digital products.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-features-section">
            <div class="features-header">
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <p>Core functionalities that make this project stand out</p>
            </div>

            <ul class="features-grid">

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Reusable UI component library</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Standardized design guidelines</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Consistent interaction patterns</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Scalable design architecture</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Cross-platform compatibility</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Interactive elements to improve engagement and exploration</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Accessible design principles</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Clear documentation structure</span>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="project-impact-section">
            <div class="impact-header">
                <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-up"></i> Results & Impact</h2>
                <p>Measurable outcomes from this project</p>
            </div>

            <ul class="impact-grid">

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Improved design consistency</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Faster development workflow</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Reduced design duplication</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Stronger system scalability</p>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="project-testimonial-section">
            <figure class="testimonial-figure">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left quote-icon"></i>

                <blockquote>
                    <p>The design system brings much-needed consistency across our digital products and significantly
                        improves efficiency for both design and development teams.</p>
                </blockquote>

                <figcaption>
                    <hr class="separator-line">
                    <strong>Carolina Esteves</strong>
                    <span>Vodafone Product Design Team</span>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>
        <!-- @import "footer" -->
    </main>

</body>

</html>